## Getting started

```bash
# 1. Copy the harness
cp -r <path-to-blueprint>/claude-config/.claude .

# 2. Copy this template, then fill in the TODO blocks above
cp <path-to-blueprint>/claude-config/CLAUDE.md.template CLAUDE.md

# 3. Copy the sacred templates
cp -r <path-to-blueprint>/docs/templates docs/templates

# 4. Verify the Hard Rules gate runs
bash .claude/skills/hard-rules-check/scripts/check-all.sh
```

